<div tabindex="-1" class="heading-wrapper level-h2"><h2 id="features">Features</h2><a class="anchor-link" href="#features"><span aria-hidden="true" class="anchor-icon"><svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path fill="currentcolor" d="m12.11 15.39-3.88 3.88a2.52 2.52 0 0 1-3.5 0 2.47 2.47 0 0 1 0-3.5l3.88-3.88a1 1 0 0 0-1.42-1.42l-3.88 3.89a4.48 4.48 0 0 0 6.33 6.33l3.89-3.88a1 1 0 1 0-1.42-1.42Zm8.58-12.08a4.49 4.49 0 0 0-6.33 0l-3.89 3.88a1 1 0 0 0 1.42 1.42l3.88-3.88a2.52 2.52 0 0 1 3.5 0 2.47 2.47 0 0 1 0 3.5l-3.88 3.88a1 1 0 1 0 1.42 1.42l3.88-3.89a4.49 4.49 0 0 0 0-6.33ZM8.83 15.17a1 1 0 0 0 1.1.22 1 1 0 0 0 .32-.22l4.92-4.92a1 1 0 0 0-1.42-1.42l-4.92 4.92a1 1 0 0 0 0 1.42Z"></path></svg></span></a></div>
<div class="feature mb-7 border-t border-t-[var(--color-cl1-gray-8)] pt-6 astro-ezsi7upz"> <h3 class="m-0 mb-2 text-[1.3125rem] leading-[1.3] font-bold tracking-[-0.02em] astro-ezsi7upz"> Key-value storage </h3> <div class="feature-description mb-3 text-base leading-[1.65] text-[var(--sl-color-text)] astro-ezsi7upz"> <p>Learn how Workers KV stores and retrieves data.</p> </div> <a href="/kv/get-started/" class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 border-b-2 border-b-[var(--color-cl1-brand-orange)] pb-px text-sm font-semibold text-[var(--sl-color-white)] no-underline transition-[border-color] duration-200 ease-in-out hover:border-b-[var(--sl-color-white)] astro-ezsi7upz"> Use Key-value storage <svg aria-hidden="true" class="astro-ezsi7upz astro-jsgs62qu" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" style="--sl-icon-size: 0.875rem;"><path d="M17.92 11.62a1.001 1.001 0 0 0-.21-.33l-5-5a1.003 1.003 0 1 0-1.42 1.42l3.3 3.29H7a1 1 0 0 0 0 2h7.59l-3.3 3.29a1.002 1.002 0 0 0 .325 1.639 1 1 0 0 0 1.095-.219l5-5a1 1 0 0 0 .21-.33 1 1 0 0 0 0-.76Z"/></svg> </a> </div>
<div class="feature mb-7 border-t border-t-[var(--color-cl1-gray-8)] pt-6 astro-ezsi7upz"> <h3 class="m-0 mb-2 text-[1.3125rem] leading-[1.3] font-bold tracking-[-0.02em] astro-ezsi7upz"> Wrangler </h3> <div class="feature-description mb-3 text-base leading-[1.65] text-[var(--sl-color-text)] astro-ezsi7upz"> <p>The Workers command-line interface, Wrangler, allows you to <a href="/workers/wrangler/commands/general/#init">create</a>, <a href="/workers/wrangler/commands/general/#dev">test</a>, and <a href="/workers/wrangler/commands/pages/#pages-deploy">deploy</a> your Workers projects.</p> </div> <a href="/workers/wrangler/install-and-update/" class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 border-b-2 border-b-[var(--color-cl1-brand-orange)] pb-px text-sm font-semibold text-[var(--sl-color-white)] no-underline transition-[border-color] duration-200 ease-in-out hover:border-b-[var(--sl-color-white)] astro-ezsi7upz"> Use Wrangler <svg aria-hidden="true" class="astro-ezsi7upz astro-jsgs62qu" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" style="--sl-icon-size: 0.875rem;"><path d="M17.92 11.62a1.001 1.001 0 0 0-.21-.33l-5-5a1.003 1.003 0 1 0-1.42 1.42l3.3 3.29H7a1 1 0 0 0 0 2h7.59l-3.3 3.29a1.002 1.002 0 0 0 .325 1.639 1 1 0 0 0 1.095-.219l5-5a1 1 0 0 0 .21-.33 1 1 0 0 0 0-.76Z"/></svg> </a> </div>
<div class="feature mb-7 border-t border-t-[var(--color-cl1-gray-8)] pt-6 astro-ezsi7upz"> <h3 class="m-0 mb-2 text-[1.3125rem] leading-[1.3] font-bold tracking-[-0.02em] astro-ezsi7upz"> Bindings </h3> <div class="feature-description mb-3 text-base leading-[1.65] text-[var(--sl-color-text)] astro-ezsi7upz"> <p>Bindings allow your Workers to interact with resources on the Cloudflare developer platform, including <a href="/r2/">R2</a>, <a href="/durable-objects/">Durable Objects</a>, and <a href="/d1/">D1</a>.</p> </div> <a href="/kv/concepts/kv-bindings/" class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 border-b-2 border-b-[var(--color-cl1-brand-orange)] pb-px text-sm font-semibold text-[var(--sl-color-white)] no-underline transition-[border-color] duration-200 ease-in-out hover:border-b-[var(--sl-color-white)] astro-ezsi7upz"> Use Bindings <svg aria-hidden="true" class="astro-ezsi7upz astro-jsgs62qu" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" style="--sl-icon-size: 0.875rem;"><path d="M17.92 11.62a1.001 1.001 0 0 0-.21-.33l-5-5a1.003 1.003 0 1 0-1.42 1.42l3.3 3.29H7a1 1 0 0 0 0 2h7.59l-3.3 3.29a1.002 1.002 0 0 0 .325 1.639 1 1 0 0 0 1.095-.219l5-5a1 1 0 0 0 .21-.33 1 1 0 0 0 0-.76Z"/></svg> </a> </div>
